    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable work car or a budget-friendly option for a first-time driver. Mechanically, it starts consistently and runs well, though it does show signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor dents, and some paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and there are some stains on the carpet, but all essential electronics and the climate control system remain functional. It has been recently serviced to ensure it is roadworthy, though a potential buyer should expect some upcoming maintenance needs typical for a car of this age.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
